<p source="GUODIAN.MUGONG 6.1. SLIPS 1-2 ">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.1">魯穆公問於子思曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.2">「何如而可謂忠臣？」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.3">子思曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.4">「恒稱其君之惡者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.5">可謂忠臣矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.6">公不悅，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-1a.7">揖而退之。</seg>
                </p>

<p source="GUODIAN.MUGONG 6.2. SLIPS 2-4, ">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.1">成孫弋見，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.2">公曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.3">「嚮者吾問忠臣於子思，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.4">子思曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.5">『恒稱其君之惡者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.6">可謂忠臣矣。』</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.7">寡人惑焉，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.8">而未之得也。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.9">成孫弋曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-2a.10">「噫，善哉，言乎！</seg>
                </p>

<p source="GUODIAN.MUGONG 6.3. SLIPS 5-7- , ">
                    <pb xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.1">夫為其君之故殺其身者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.2">嘗有之矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.3">恒稱其君之惡者,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.4">未之有也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.5">夫為其君之故殺其身者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.6">效祿爵者也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.7">恒 [稱其君] 之惡 [者，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.8">遠] 祿爵者[ 也].</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.9">[為] 義而遠祿爵，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.10">非 子思，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0019_tls_001-3a.11">吾惡聞之矣。」</seg>
                </p>

